---
import ElevateLayout from "../../../layouts/ElevateLayout.astro";
import Header from "../../../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../../../components/Footer.astro";
---

<ElevateLayout
  title="Cities I'd Go Back To"
  description="The cities I would go back to — not because I missed something, but because I know how to be there."
>
  <Header />

  <main>
    <section class="cities-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="eyebrow">
          <a href="/elevate-your-travel/" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:none;">← Elevate Your Travel</a>
        </p>
        <h1>Cities I'd Go Back To</h1>
        <p class="cities-hero__lead">
          There are plenty of places I still want to see. But these are different. These are the cities I would go
          back to — not because I missed something, but because I know how to be there. Where the rhythm makes
          sense, and I know where to eat, where to go, and how to spend a day without overthinking it.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="city-entries">
      <div class="city-entry">
        <div class="city-entry__photo">
          <img
            src="/images/city-guides/sydney.jpg"
            alt="Sydney, Australia — coastal landscape"
            width="960"
            height="640"
            loading="eager"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="city-entry__body">
          <span class="city-entry__eyebrow">Sydney, Australia</span>
          <h2 class="city-entry__name">Sydney</h2>
          <p class="city-entry__tagline">Southern California, just done better</p>
          <p class="city-entry__text">
            It feels familiar in the best way. Beach mornings, long afternoons, and a slower pace that never feels
            forced.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="city-entry">
        <div class="city-entry__photo">
          <img
            src="/images/city-guides/london.jpg"
            alt="London, England — street scene"
            width="768"
            height="1024"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="city-entry__body">
          <span class="city-entry__eyebrow">London, England</span>
          <h2 class="city-entry__name">London</h2>
          <p class="city-entry__tagline">Pub culture that carries the day</p>
          <p class="city-entry__text">
            There is something about being in another country that speaks your language but feels completely
            different. Old pubs, proper pints, and the ability to let the day unfold without much of a plan.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="city-entry">
        <div class="city-entry__photo">
          <img src="/images/city-guides/paris.jpg" alt="Paris, France" width="768" height="1024" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="city-entry__body">
          <span class="city-entry__eyebrow">Paris, France</span>
          <h2 class="city-entry__name">Paris</h2>
          <p class="city-entry__tagline">Shopping that ends in food</p>
          <p class="city-entry__text">
            I go for the shopping, but not for anything you would expect. I leave with cheese, butter, wine, and
            mustard instead of clothing.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="city-entry">
        <div class="city-entry__photo">
          <img src="/images/city-guides/tokyo.jpg" alt="Tokyo, Japan" width="576" height="820" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="city-entry__body">
          <span class="city-entry__eyebrow">Tokyo, Japan</span>
          <h2 class="city-entry__name">Tokyo</h2>
          <p class="city-entry__tagline">Clean, efficient, and endlessly good to eat</p>
          <p class="city-entry__text">
            The city runs smoothly, the food is consistently excellent, and there is always something new worth
            finding.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="city-entry">
        <div class="city-entry__photo">
          <img
            src="/images/city-guides/san-diego.jpg"
            alt="San Diego, United States"
            width="683"
            height="1024"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="city-entry__body">
          <span class="city-entry__eyebrow">San Diego, United States</span>
          <h2 class="city-entry__name">San Diego</h2>
          <p class="city-entry__tagline">Weather and a pace that never rushes you</p>
          <p class="city-entry__text">
            It is hard to beat the combination of perfect weather and a city that does not feel like it is trying
            too hard. Beach days, casual meals, and a rhythm that makes everything feel simple.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="city-entry">
        <div class="city-entry__photo">
          <img
            src="/images/city-guides/steamboat-springs.jpg"
            alt="Steamboat Springs, Colorado"
            width="738"
            height="982"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="city-entry__body">
          <span class="city-entry__eyebrow">Steamboat Springs, Colorado</span>
          <h2 class="city-entry__name">Steamboat Springs</h2>
          <p class="city-entry__tagline">A ski weekend you already know how to do</p>
          <p class="city-entry__text">
            Knowing the mountain, the town, and where to eat changes everything. It turns a trip into a routine, and
            that is what makes it worth going back to.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section class="dreaming-cta">
      <div class="container dreaming-cta__inner">
        <div>
          <h3>Want to go deeper on any of these?</h3>
          <p>
            City guides, itineraries, and the details that make a trip worth taking — built from real experience.
          </p>
        </div>
        <a class="button button--primary" href="/city-guides/">Explore the Guides</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</ElevateLayout>
